<h1>Changelog</h1>
<h2>v3.0.3 (2025-12-16)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Update sub-dependencies to their latest stable releases</li>
</ul>
<h2>v3.0.2 (2025-12-15)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Update dependencies to their latest stable releases</li>
</ul>
<h2>v3.0.1 (2025-07-10)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>The Authorization API app is now available for UCS 5.2.</li>
</ul>
<h2>v3.0.0 (2024-12-16)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>The Authorization API now uses the UDM attributes guardianRoles and guardianInheritedRoles instead of guardianRole.</li>
</ul>
<h2>v2.0.3 (2024-04-17)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>The app installation has been simplified and doesn't need additional steps anymore</li>
</ul>
<h2>v2.0.2 (2024-03-26)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Add service entry for Guardian Authorization API to host server in UDM.</li>
</ul>
<h2>v2.0.1 (2024-01-22)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Fix a problem, where contexts are not processed correctly.</li>
</ul>
<h2>v2.0.0 (2024-01-15)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Remove App Center settings containing secrets.</li>
    <li>Use Machine Account for UDM access.</li>
    <li>The application can now only be installed on the UCS system roles primary and backup.</li>
    <li>Fix container startup behavior.</li>
    <li>Update Keycloak configuration.</li>
</ul>
<h2>v1.1.0 (2023-12-22)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Remove obsolete App Center settings.</li>
    <li>Migrate docker image to UCS base image.</li>
</ul>
<h2>v1.0.0 (2023-12-11)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Initial release.</li>
</ul>
